last_episode_to_air.name: Epic Rager
last_episode_to_air.overview: Huck amps up the fun at the annual Jellystone block party by inviting a bunch of party cavemen.

name: Jellystone!
overview: Welcome to Jellystone! Travel to a magical town where you’ll meet new and old friends, including Yogi Bear, Cindy Bear, Boo Boo, and Huckleberry Hound…and Jabberjaw and Top Cat and Snagglepuss and El Kabong and Wally Gator and Johnny Quest and Hadji and Shag Rugg and Captain Caveman and a whole lot more.

episodes.name: Yogi's Tummy Troubles / Gorilla in Our Midst
episodes.overview: Cindy accidentally turns Yogi into an unstoppable eating machine after installing a nuclear stomach in him. When Grape Ape falls asleep in the middle of town square, it's up to the citizens of Jellystone to move this mountain!

episodes.name: Boo Boots / My Doggie Dave
episodes.overview: Feeling unappreciated, Boo Boo gets a boost from a new pair of boots, but Yogi grows jealous of Boo Boo's newfound popularity. When Doggie Daddy brings a disguised Augie to his guy's night, she becomes the most popular member of the group.

episodes.name: A Coconut to Remember / Grocery Store
episodes.overview: When Magilla gets amnesia, Jabberjaw exploits him to score her dream job as assistant manager of the store. After Augie and Daddy forget a crucial ingredient while shopping, Augie embarks on a journey to retrieve those bananas.

episodes.name: Must Be Jelly / Cats Do Dance
episodes.overview: Cindy turns everyone into gelatin in order to finish her book club reading. Top Cat and the gang might actually have to do some hard work. After losing their alley in a dance battle, Top Cat and the gang might actually have to do some hard work to get it back.

episodes.name: VIP Baby You Know Me / El Kabong's Kabong is Gone
episodes.overview: Shag wants to live a VIP lifestyle but borrowing Mudbug Cafe's money turns out to be a mistake. El Kabong must replace his broken guitar.

episodes.name: Mr. Flabby Dabby Wabby Jabby / Ice Ice Daddy
episodes.overview: The kids go to a grownup movie in disguise, but things get out of hand when they're mistaken for the real Mr. Flabby Dabby Wabby Jabby. After realizing he's a father, Captain Caveman dedicates himself to being the best dad.

episodes.name: DNA, A-OK! / Face of the Town!
episodes.overview: After finding out he's 98% cat, Yogi tries to roll with Top Cat and his gang, but he has a hard time fitting in. Mayor Huckleberry holds a contest to find the new face of Jellystone.

episodes.name: Catanooga Cheese Explosion / Squish or Miss
episodes.overview: Yogi strikes a deal with Shag Rugg so he can get into Cheese-Is-Us. Augie and the rest of the Jellystone kids try to help Yakky be braver.

episodes.name: Gotta Kiss Them All / Jelly Wrestle Rumble!
episodes.overview: When Augie and Yakky discover a fun VR game while repairing Ruff and Ready, they wind up blurring the lines between fiction and reality. Huckleberry hosts a wrestling tournament so Funky Phantom can relive his glory days.

episodes.name: A Fish Sticky Situation / A Town Video: Welcome to Jellystone
episodes.overview: Top Cat and his gang are in for a smelly surprise when they try to resell expired fish sticks. Huckleberry hires Yogi to direct a town tourism video.

episodes.name: Spell Book
episodes.overview: Augie, Yakky, and Shag help an overworked Winsome Witch prepare for Halloween ... but end up making things worse!

episodes.name: Lady Danjjer: Is It Wrong to Long for Kabong?
episodes.overview: Jabberjaw realizes that she’ll need to become a supervillain if she wants to get El Kabong’s attention.

episodes.name: Baby Shenanigans
episodes.overview: Augie, Shag, and Yakky accidentally turn everyone in Jellystone into babies in hopes of having other kids to play with.

episodes.name: Bleep
episodes.overview: When an alien crashes into her lab, a lonely Cindy suddenly finds herself with a new best friend.

episodes.name: Yogi's Midlife Crisis
episodes.overview: After starting a rock band, Yogi is quickly outshined by Squiddly Diddly.

episodes.name: Jellystone Moon Platoon
episodes.overview: Mayor Huck assembles a team of astronauts to save the world from an impending cosmic disaster.

episodes.name: The Sea Monster of Jellystone Cove
episodes.overview: To get their own space at the beach, Jabberjaw and Loopy De Loop decide to dress up like sea monsters.

episodes.name: Business
episodes.overview: Augie starts her own business – just like her hero, Bobbie Looey

episodes.name: Pants
episodes.overview: Magilla starts to feel out of touch when a silly new fashion fad sweeps through Jellystone.

episodes.name: Uh Oh! It's a Burglar!
episodes.overview: Jabberjaw and Loopy attempt to thwart a spooky nighttime burglary at Magilla’s clothing store.

episodes.name: It's a Mad Mad Mad Rat Race
episodes.overview: Jellystone is torn apart by a frantic search for Lippy the Lion and Hardy Har Har’s misplaced treasure.

episodes.name: The Brave Little Daddy
episodes.overview: When Doggy Daddy is tasked with stopping Grape Ape from terrorizing the town, a misunderstanding spirals out of control!

episodes.name: The Big Stink
episodes.overview: When the Jellystone Stink Factory has a catastrophic meltdown, it’s up to Yogi Bear, Doggy Daddy, and Mildew Wolf to save everyone.

episodes.name: Boo-Boo and Benny: Little Buddy Trouble
episodes.overview: After Boo Boo and Benny discover they have a ton in common and become friends, Yogi starts to miss his best buddy.

episodes.name: The Box Thief
episodes.overview: When packages begin disappearing, discount detectives Snooper and Blabber are called in to help find the culprit!

episodes.name: Jailcation
episodes.overview: Hoping to land in a swanky, high-end jail, Top Cat’s gang try their best to get arrested.

episodes.name: Balloon Kids
episodes.overview: Augie, Yakky, and Shag help Peter on a delivery run in his airship – but everything goes wrong!

episodes.name: Augie's Baby
episodes.overview: After accidentally trapping Yakky inside a watermelon, Augie convinces herself that it’s come to life as a baby.

episodes.name: Heroes and Capes
episodes.overview: When everyone in town becomes a superhero, El Kabong begins to wonder if he’s needed anymore.

episodes.name: Sweet Dreams
episodes.overview: When Augie has a bad dream, Doggie Daddy and others entertain her with random stories.

episodes.name: Meet the Jetsons
episodes.overview: Jellystone heroes travel to the future to save the town from out-of-control robots.

episodes.name: Disco Fever
episodes.overview: An uncontrollable 70’s dance craze infects Jellystone and it’s up to Cindy, Yogi, and Boo Boo to stop it.

episodes.name: Cindy vs Noodle Arms
episodes.overview: Cindy teams up with Top Cat to fix everyone’s wobbly arms.

episodes.name: Hot Guys, Cold Turkey
episodes.overview: Jabberjaw has an overactive cupid which makes her fall in love with everyone and everything.

episodes.name: Lotions 11
episodes.overview: With Top Cat in jail, his gang must pull off the scam of the century without him!

episodes.name: The LAFF Games
episodes.overview: Jellystone goes head to head in a competition against their rival town, New Bedrock.

episodes.name: Frankenhooky
episodes.overview: Yogi and Boo Boo play hooky from work at an old, abandoned fun park where some meddling kids mistake them for monsters.

episodes.name: Girl, You My Friend!
episodes.overview: Cindy, Jabberjaw, and Squiddly compete for the title of "best friend" in Jellystone.

episodes.name: Jellystone Noir
episodes.overview: Shag hires a bunch of detectives to find his lost sense of childhood wonder.

episodes.name: Vote Raspberry
episodes.overview: Huck creates a fake opponent to run against him in the mayoral election.

episodes.name: Collection Protection
episodes.overview: Augie, Shag, and Yakky guard Peter’s collection of valuable toys while he leaves town.

episodes.name: Mummy Knows Best
episodes.overview: An injured El Kabong mistakenly hires a cursed mummy to take over his teaching duties.

episodes.name: Augie-mented Reality
episodes.overview: Doggy Daddy transforms a bunch of folks into Augie so he can spend even more time with her.

episodes.name: Space Con
episodes.overview: Peter Potamus’ convention costume gets him mistaken for the real Space Ghost.

episodes.name: Sha-zogi
episodes.overview: Yogi gives Shazzan a break from work by taking on his genie powers for the day.

episodes.name: Li'l Honk Honks
episodes.overview: After Shag discovers his Dad’s old racing car toys, everyone in town excitedly gets into racing each other with the tiny cars.

episodes.name: Epic Rager
episodes.overview: Huck amps up the fun at the annual Jellystone block party by inviting a bunch of party cavemen.
